      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:42",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但我们公务员也不是一直都闲着的 也有拼命加班的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "哦哦 我想你这个点应该也是不忙的 和昨天差不多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我没别的意思 你不用那么说的滴水不漏吧hh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:43",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道你们公务员也有加班 任务很重的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我有几个公务员的同学会和我抱怨",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没办法啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:44",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "谁让互联网上大家对公务员的刻板印象那么深呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是不提前说明 别人还以为我拿了纳税人的钱天天摸鱼呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那你们都会忙什么呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？你好奇这个？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好奇啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我的朋友没有在市委办的 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:46",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "再说了  工作的城市不同 服务内容也不同吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "服务这个词说的好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然我不是干窗口的市政厅的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:47",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但我的工作内容基本上也就是给其他的公务员工作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "筹备筹备什么党会啊  起草红头文件啊 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我的案头工作会很多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "市委办具体落实下来的工作那么琐碎吗？\n",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我之前对市委办的概念一直是综合机构，核心部门",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没错啊 做这些事很核心啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:49",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没有我们把市里的最新政策传达下去 乡镇怎么收到指示呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh你说的你们好像是电话一样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "说得太对了哥们",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:50",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我们市委办的作用就是这个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "刚工作的时候我经常觉得自己好像一个电话  谁都可以把我拎起来嚷嚷两句",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你这个比喻好熟悉的感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:51",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好有东北人的幽默 你是东北的吗？",
