      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你毕竟是搞教育的 不难猜的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "据我所知 这些年互联网上最出名的东北作家就是东北三杰",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "10:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是双雪涛吗？但是他的嘴好像没那么贫",
