      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "16:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "漫才兄弟哥们也略有涉猎哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "16:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的涉猎范围也很广啊",
