      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "16:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "话说你觉得自己算文青吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "16:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "一半一半吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "16:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "主要现在的语境之下  文青显得很像是在骂人的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false,
      "timestamp": "16:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯 理解 经过这几年网络环境的话语重塑",
